            "custom_liquid": "<div style=\"padding: 12px; text-align: left; background-color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 15px; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">🌿 Calms on contact</span> – Guaiazulene-tinted blue clay cools the skin and soothes irritation while it works.<br><br>\n<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">💧 Triple-acid complex</span> – AHA, BHA, and PHA lift blackheads from inside the pore without over-drying.<br><br>\n<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">⏱ Three-minute treatment</span> – Visibly tighter pores in under five minutes. Once or twice a week.<br><br>\n<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">🧴 Five clays, no fillers</span> – A mineral-rich blend that gently exfoliates without stripping sensitive skin.\n</div>"
